{"tid":106784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑 Channel:  「社會撕裂、停滯不前」由林鄭把口講出黎很荒謬","createTime":"2017-02-04T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T10:28:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87dcc58f1906887aebfafa5611fc0495d365d6c2","tid":106784,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"陶傑 Channel<br />\n12 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在「參選分享會」中說：「我們的社會撕裂，我們的社會停滯不前。」<br />\n<br />\n此一口吻，好似一個外人。阿姐：但過去五年，你是政務司司長，香港一切「撕裂」和「停滯」，完全與你無關？<br />\n<br />\n過去的撕裂和停滯，發生在「梁林鄭體制」的五年，而林鄭聲稱「將延續梁振英管治理念」，咁咪即是你做了特首，會延續香港的撕裂，香港社會將繼續停滯不前？<br />\n<br />\nSimple logic：咁點解香港人要支持你？"},{"pid":"31163a2cabf4b80922dbe72cd3afc6fb5b3e04b5","tid":106784,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a4fa425454aee95bc6c0574b0552cfdc1ceb32","tid":106784,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44694cfc143c00b0b93434828a57a892654389d5","tid":106784,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f6379a089ed4aed69441230a4d574d103147b","tid":106784,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"689 2.0表示社會撕裂唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2469e856e24bfb333cb175bd6af7ea20034a5059","tid":106784,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:39:19.0